ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHV/107%2c%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a%e6%9b%b4%e4%b8%80%2c67%2c20220726%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHV,107,重上更一,67,20220726,1","JYEAR":"107","JCASE":"重上更一","JNO":"67","JDATE":"20220726","JTITLE":"給付學收款"}